[Student "S"]
{WEST has a 11 points with both Minors and she doesn't want to sell out to SOUTH's 2\S. 
So she makes a Negative Double, effectively bidding both minors at once.

EAST has four \Cs so he bids the suit at the minimum level and WEST passes.}

